Class WeatherObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • database.WeatherObject

  • public class WeatherObject
extends java.lang.Object
    WeatherObject creates an object that can be used to query the collected data.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      WeatherObject()
      If the Constructor is called without any Parameters, the object can only be used to query the devices that have connected to the base station

      Constructor for a WeatherObject object if one of the unites is set to zero, only functions that do not need the specific unite for their call can be used.
